Python Fundamentals — Coding Challenges
Complete coding challenges on three platforms to solidify your Python skills. Save your solutions and push them to your GitHub repository.
a. Informatics.msk.ru — https://informatics.msk.ru/
Input/Output, Assignment Operators — problems A–E
Conditional Statements — problems A–E
Loops:
